{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Metal Goat|kanji=辛未|romaji=kanoto hitsuji|onyomi=shimmu|p=xīnwèi|w=hsin-wei|mi=ɕin⁵³ weɪ̯⁵³|y=san1 mei6|j=san1 mei6|ci=sɐn mei²|mc=sin mjɨjH|oc-bs=sin məɯʔ|qq=}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}} '''Yin Metal Goat''', also known as {{ill|Xīnwèi|ja|辛未|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}（Kanoto-hitsuji, Shinkin-no-hitsuji, Shinbi）, is one of the combinations in the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|干支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.
It is the 8th combination in the Sexagenary cycle, following {{ill|Gēngwǔ|ja|庚午|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and preceding {{ill|Rénshēn|ja|壬申|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. In the {{ill|Yin-Yang and Five Elements theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|Xīn|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} represents Yin {{ill|Metal|ja|金|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branch|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|Wèi|ja|未|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} represents Yin {{ill|Earth|ja|土|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, forming a {{ill|Generating Cycle (Wuxing)|ja|相生|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (Earth generating Metal).
== Xīnwèi Years == A year in the {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} where the remainder when divided by 60 is 11 is a Xīnwèi year.
{| class="wikitable" |+'''Xīnwèi Years''' |- ![[1st Millennium]]!![[2nd Millennium]]!![[3rd Millennium]] |- | *[[11]] *[[71]] *[[131]] *[[191]] *[[251]] *[[311]] *[[371]] *[[431]] *[[491]] *[[551]] *[[611]] *[[671]] *[[731]] *[[791]] *[[851]] *[[911]] *[[971]] | *[[1031]] *[[1091]] *[[1151]] *[[1211]] *[[1271]] *[[1331]] *[[1391]] *[[1451]] *[[1511]] *[[1571]] *[[1631]] *[[1691]] *[[1751]] *[[1811]] *[[1871]] *[[1931]] *[[1991]] | *[[2051]] *[[2111]] *[[2171]] *[[2231]] *[[2291]] *[[2351]] *[[2411]] *[[2471]] *[[2531]] *[[2591]] *[[2651]] *[[2711]] *[[2771]] *[[2831]] *[[2891]] *[[2951]] |}
== Xīnwèi Months == In a Gregorian year where the last digit is 4 or 9 (corresponding to {{ill|Jiǎ|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or {{ill|Jǐ|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} in the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}), the {{ill|6th Month|ja|6月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} is a Xīnwèi month. However, in certain cases, the calculation is based on the {{ill|Lunar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or the {{ill|Solar Terms|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (from {{ill|Lesser Heat|ja|小暑|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Beginning of Autumn|ja|立秋|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}).
== Xīnwèi Days == Xīnwèi days have specific meanings in the {{ill|Selected Days|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} system.
=== Selected Days === A Xīnwèi day is the second day of the {{ill|Great Earth Period|ja|犯土|lt=大土|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. ==See Also== *{{prefix|qq=}} *{{intitle|qq=}}
