{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Metal Goat|kanji=辛未|romaji=kanoto hitsuji|onyomi=shimmu|p=xīnwèi|w=hsin-wei|mi=ɕin⁵³ weɪ̯⁵³|y=san1 mei6|j=san1 mei6|ci=sɐn mei²|mc=sin mjɨjH|oc-bs=sin məɯʔ|qq=}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}} '''Yin Metal Goat''', also known as {{ill|Xīnwèi|ja|1=Yin Metal Goat|2=ja|辛未|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xīnwèi|qq=}}（Kanoto-hitsuji, Shinkin-no-hitsuji, Shinbi）, is one of the combinations in the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|干支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.
It is the 8th combination in the Sexagenary cycle, following {{ill|Gēngwǔ|ja|庚午|1=Yang Metal Horse|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gēngwǔ|qq=}} and preceding {{ill|Rénshēn|ja|1=Yang Water Monkey|2=ja|壬申|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rénshēn|qq=}}. In the {{ill|Yin-Yang and Five Elements theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Five Elements theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stem|qq=}} {{ill|Xīn|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|lt=Kanoto (辛)|2=ja|3=辛|4=zh|5=辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xīn|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=}} represents Yin {{ill|Metal|ja|金|1=Metal (wuxing)|lt=Metal (金)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Metal|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branch|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branch|qq=}} {{ill|Wèi|ja|未|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wèi|qq=}} represents Yin {{ill|Earth|ja|土|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|qq=}}, forming a {{ill|Generating Cycle (Wuxing)|ja|相生|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Generating Cycle (Wuxing)|qq=}} (Earth generating Metal).
== Xīnwèi Years == A year in the {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} where the remainder when divided by 60 is 11 is a Xīnwèi year.
{| class="wikitable" |+'''Xīnwèi Years''' |- ![[1st Millennium]]!![[2nd Millennium]]!![[3rd Millennium]] |- | *[[11]] *[[71]] *[[131]] *[[191]] *[[251]] *[[311]] *[[371]] *[[431]] *[[491]] *[[551]] *[[611]] *[[671]] *[[731]] *[[791]] *[[851]] *[[911]] *[[971]] | *[[1031]] *[[1091]] *[[1151]] *[[1211]] *[[1271]] *[[1331]] *[[1391]] *[[1451]] *[[1511]] *[[1571]] *[[1631]] *[[1691]] *[[1751]] *[[1811]] *[[1871]] *[[1931]] *[[1991]] | *[[2051]] *[[2111]] *[[2171]] *[[2231]] *[[2291]] *[[2351]] *[[2411]] *[[2471]] *[[2531]] *[[2591]] *[[2651]] *[[2711]] *[[2771]] *[[2831]] *[[2891]] *[[2951]] |}
== Xīnwèi Months == In a Gregorian year where the last digit is 4 or 9 (corresponding to {{ill|Jiǎ|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|lt=Kinoe (甲)|2=ja|3=甲|4=zh|5=甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jiǎ|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=}} or {{ill|Jǐ|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|lt=Tsuchinoto (己)|2=ja|3=己|4=zh|5=己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jǐ|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=}} in the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}}), the {{ill|6th Month|ja|6月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/6th Month|qq=}} is a Xīnwèi month. However, in certain cases, the calculation is based on the {{ill|Lunar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or the {{ill|Solar Terms|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar Terms|qq=}} (from {{ill|Lesser Heat|ja|小暑|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lesser Heat|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Beginning of Autumn|ja|立秋|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Beginning of Autumn|qq=}}).
== Xīnwèi Days == Xīnwèi days have specific meanings in the {{ill|Selected Days|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Selected Days|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} system.
