== Xīnwèi Months == In a Gregorian year where the last digit is 4 or 9 (corresponding to {{ill|Jiǎ|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|lt=Kinoe (甲)|2=ja|3=甲|4=zh|5=甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jiǎ|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jiǎ|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=}} or {{ill|Jǐ|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|lt=Tsuchinoto (己)|2=ja|3=己|4=zh|5=己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jǐ|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jǐ|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=}} in the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}}), the {{ill|6th Month|ja|6月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/6th Month|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/6th Month|qq=}} is a Xīnwèi month. However, in certain cases, the calculation is based on the {{ill|Lunar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or the {{ill|Solar Terms|ja|二十四節気|1=Solar term|2=ja|3=二十四節気|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar Terms|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar Terms|qq=}} (from {{ill|Lesser Heat|ja|小暑|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lesser Heat|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lesser Heat|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Beginning of Autumn|ja|立秋|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Beginning of Autumn|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Beginning of Autumn|qq=}}).
