thly Branches|Earthly Branch]] {{ill|Wèi|ja|未|1=Goat (Zodiac)|lt=Goat (未)|2=ja|3=未|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wèi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wèi|13=User:Immanuelle/Goat (Zodiac)|qq=}} represents Yin {{ill|Earth|ja|Earth (土)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|zh|Earth (土)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|lt=Earth (土)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|1=Earth (wuxing)|zh|Earth (土)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|lt=Earth (土)|lt=Earth (土)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth (wuxing)|zh|Earth (土)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|lt=Earth (土)|qq=}}, forming a [[:en:Aioi|Generating Cycle (Wuxing)]] (Earth generating Metal).
==Pronunciation== * English: Yin Metal Goat (辛未) ** Chinese (Mandarin Pinyin): xīnwèi ** Cantonese (Jyutping): san1 mei6 ** Japanese: ***Kunyomi 1: Kanoto-hitsuji ***Kunyomi 2: Shinkin-no-hitsuji ***Onyomi 1: shinbi ** Korean (Revised Romanization, Hangul): sinmi (신미) ** Vietnamese (Hán-Việt): Tân Mùi
<!-- == * Yin Metal Goat (辛未) ** Chinese (Mandarin Pinyin): xīnwèi ** Cantonese (Jyutping): san1 mei6 ** Japanese: ***Kunyomi: かのとひつじ (kanoto-hitsuji) ***Onyomi: しんきんのひつじ (shinkin-no-hitsuji) ***Onyomi: しんび (shinbi) ** Korean (Revised Romanization): sinmi ** Vietnamese (Hán-Việt): Tân Mùi
--> ==Years of Yin Metal Goat== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] where the remainder when divided by 60 is 11 is a Xīnwèi year.
{| class="wikitable" |+'''Xīnwèi Years''' |- ![[1st Millennium]]!![[2nd Millennium]]!![[3rd Millennium]] |- | *[[:en:Qq|Qq]] *[[71]] *[[131]] *[[191]] *[[251]] *[[311]] *[[371]] *[[431]] *[[491]] *[[551]] *[[611]] *[[671]] *[[731]] *[[791]] *[[851]] *[[911]] *[[971]] | *[[:en:1031|1031]] *[[:en:1091|1091]] *[[:en:1151|1151]] *[[:en:1211|1211]] *[[1271]] *[[1331]] *[[1391]] *[[1451]] *[[1511]] *[[1571]] *[[1631]] *[[1691]] *[[1751]] *[[1811]] *[[1871]] *[[1931]] *[[1991]] | *[[2051]] *[[2111]] *[[2171]] *[[2231]] *[[2291]] *[[2351]] *[[2411]] *[[2471]] *[[2531]] *[[2591]] *[[2651]] *[[2711]] *[[2771]] *[[2831]] *[[2891]] *[[2951]] |}
==Months of Yin Metal Goat== In a Gregorian year where the last digit is 4 or 9 (corresponding to {{ill|Jiǎ|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|lt=Kinoe (甲)|2=ja|3=甲|4=zh|5=甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jiǎ|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jiǎ|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (甲)|qq=}} or {{ill|Jǐ|ja|己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|lt=Tsuchinoto (己)|2=ja|3=己|4=zh|5=己|1=Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jǐ|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jǐ|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (己)|qq=}} in the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]]), the [[:en:June|6th Month]] is a Xīnwèi month. However, in certain cases, the calculation is based on the {{ill|Lunar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or the [[:en:Solar term|Solar term]] (from [[:en:Xiaoshu|Lesser Heat]] to the day before [[:en:Liqiu|Beginning of Autumn]]).
==Days of Yin Metal Goat== Xīnwèi days have specific meanings in the {{ill|Selected Days|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Selected Days|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Selected Days|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} system.
=== Selected Days === A Xīnwèi day is the second day of the {{ill|Great Earth Period|ja|犯土|lt=大土|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Great Earth Period|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Great Earth Period|qq=}}. ==See Also== *{{prefix|qq=}} *{{intitle|qq=}}
